sources.description:
*Clare And Francis* - Chiara, and her sister, Agnes collaborate with Francesco, founded the Order of Poor Ladies and the Friars Minor. In 1223, on the way back in Umbria, Francis and brother Illuminated friend stop before Christmas in Greccio, near Viterbo, where they build what will be the first nativity scene in the history of the Christian Church.
2007.  Stars: Ettore Bassi, Maria P. Petruolo, Gabriele Cirilli
